# Chain Routing

1. Resolve chain via `registry/chains.json` or `lib.chain_providers.resolve_chain()`.
2. Route to MCP server by VM family (evm-rpc-server, solana-rpc-server, etc.).
3. Validate addresses per chain format before RPC calls.
4. Include confidence score (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW) in every operation response.
